[src:jackson-json-java/serialization] The predicate `write_term/3` is standardized in the ISO Specification for Prolog (ISO/IEC 13211-1) on pages 59 ff.
[src:jackson-json-java/serialization] Therefore it is expected that terms serialized-out by one implementation can be serialized-in by another without ambiguity or surprises.
[src:jackson-json-java/serialization] In practice, implementation-specific extensions (e.g.
